568
00:36:12,837 --> 00:36:14,361
Cameron, vamos.

569
00:36:15,439 --> 00:36:17,168
Vamos, vamos.

570
00:36:28,119 --> 00:36:29,552
PapeI.

571
00:36:31,822 --> 00:36:34,086
