642
00:42:44,094 --> 00:42:46,255
Venha, "Abe".

643
00:42:46,797 --> 00:42:48,321
Chame Abe Froman.

644
00:42:48,432 --> 00:42:51,663
- Chez Quis, bonjour.
- Posso falar com Abe Froman...

645
00:42:52,603 --> 00:42:56,039
- o rei da lingüiça de Chicago?
- Abe Froman?

646
00:42:56,707 --> 00:42:58,937
Deixe-me ver no restaurante.

647
00:42:59,043 --> 00:43:01,409
Pode descrevê-lo para mim, por favor?

648
00:43:01,812 --> 00:43:05,612
Jaqueta de couro,
